Migration.Name: Adempiere-302 Add Bank Deposit Document
Migration.Comments: Add a bank deposit document that can record payments and cash deposits to a bank account and be reconciled as a single transaction on a bank statement.

There are two reasons for de-activating and not deleting records: (1) The system requires the record for audit purposes. (2) The record is referenced by other records. Step.Comments: Add Bank Deposits to validation rule

PO.Data: C_Payment not in BankStatement or BankDeposit

Data.oldValue: NOT EXISTS (SELECT * FROM C_BankStatementLine bsl INNER JOIN C_BankStatement bs ON (bsl.C_BankStatement_ID=bs.C_BankStatement_ID) WHERE bsl.C_Payment_ID=C_Payment.C_Payment_ID AND bs.DocStatus<>'VO') AND C_Payment.DocStatus IN ('CO','CL','RE') AND C_Payment.PayAmt<>0 AND C_Payment.IsReconciled='N' AND C_Payment.C_BankAccount_ID=@C_BankAccount_ID@

PO.Data: NOT EXISTS (SELECT * FROM C_BankStatementLine bsl INNER JOIN C_BankStatement bs ON (bsl.C_BankStatement_ID=bs.C_BankStatement_ID) WHERE bsl.C_Payment_ID=C_Payment.C_Payment_ID AND bs.DocStatus<>'VO') AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT * FROM C_BankDepositLine bdl INNER JOIN C_BankDeposit bd ON (bdl.C_BankDeposit_ID=bd.C_BankDeposit_ID) WHERE bdl.C_Payment_ID=C_Payment.C_Payment_ID AND bd.DocStatus<>'VO') AND C_Payment.DocStatus IN ('CO','CL','RE') AND C_Payment.PayAmt<>0 AND C_Payment.IsReconciled='N' AND C_Payment.C_BankAccount_ID=@C_BankAccount_ID@

The Process Bank Deposit window allows you to create Deposits that will ease the reconciliation of your Bank Statements where deposits of many items show as a single entry in the bank statement. You can either enter the line items that are included in the Deposit Line tab or select the ''Create From'' button to automatically generate the deposit from all unreconciled payments to this bank account. Once you have completed the deposit, select the ''Process Deposit'' button to mark the deposited items as reconciled and create a deposit entry that can be reconciled with the bank statement.
The bank deposit is a summary of the deposited items.
